OL,3,CMPs criticise 'negligent' Labour over
OL,4,Ccuts to adoption support
OL,6,FA group of West Country MPs has
OL,7,Faccused the government of being
OL,8,F"beyond negligent" over cuts to
OL,9,Fspecialist support for adopted
OL,10,Fchildren, claiming the "terrifying"
OL,11,Fchanges were "sneaked out" over Easter.
OL,13,FFor a decade, the Adoption and
OL,14,FSpecialist Guardianship Support Fund
OL,15,F(ASGSF) has helped thousands of
OL,16,Ffamilies cover the costs of services
OL,17,Flike psychotherapy, to help young
OL,18,Fadopted people cope with past traumas.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
