OL,3,CMPs criticise 'negligent' Labour over
OL,4,Ccuts to adoption support
OL,6,FUp until March this year, local
OL,7,Fauthorities and adoption agencies
OL,8,Fcould apply for #5,000 per year per
OL,9,Fchild for therapy and #2,500 a year
OL,10,Ffor assessments.
OL,12,FLabour has kept the overall budget the
OL,13,Fsame, but has changed how it will be
OL,14,Fallocated. The #5,000 therapy grant
OL,15,Fhas been cut to #3,000 and the
OL,16,Fseparate #2,500 allowance has been
OL,17,Faltogether scrapped.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
