OL,3,CMPs criticise 'negligent' Labour over
OL,4,Ccuts to adoption support
OL,6,F"We are asking people to care for the
OL,7,Fmost vulnerable children and if we
OL,8,Fdon't give them the tools to do that,
OL,9,Fthey won't apply in the first place,"
OL,10,Fsaid South West Devon's Conservative
OL,11,FMP, Rebecca Smith.
OL,13,F"There is a very real concern that the
OL,14,Fnumber of adoptions will fall and more
OL,15,Fchildren, those with some of the most
OL,16,Fdifficult and challenging stories,
OL,17,Fwill face the long term in care,
OL,18,Fseeing their futures massively
OL,19,Fimpacted as a result."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
