OL,3,CMPs criticise 'negligent' Labour over
OL,4,Ccuts to adoption support
OL,6,FAccording to the government, the
OL,7,Fdecision to change the rules around
OL,8,FASGSF was made "in a challenging
OL,9,Ffiscal climate" and aims to "maximise
OL,10,Fthe number of children who can access
OL,11,Fthe fund".
OL,13,FBut Edward Morello, West Dorset's
OL,14,FLiberal Democrat MP, said it's a
OL,15,F"fundamental problem" that the funding
OL,16,Ffor ongoing support "no longer exists".
OL,18,FAmid the criticism of the decision was
OL,19,Fan attack on how the changes were
OL,20,Fannounced.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
