OL,7,F"overnight" and families were given no
OL,8,Fwarning or time to prepare - a claim
OL,9,FLabour fought back against.
OL,11,FOthers predicted that reduced support
OL,12,Fcould end up costing the government
OL,13,Fmore in future.
