OL,3,CMPs criticise 'negligent' Labour over
OL,4,Ccuts to adoption support
OL,6,FCameron Thomas, Lib Dem MP for
OL,7,FTewkesbury, said: "Diminishing this
OL,8,Fsupport will have long-term financial
OL,9,Fimpacts on the government's
OL,10,Fforthcoming budget", while South
OL,11,FDevon's MP Caroline Voaden advised
OL,12,Fearly therapeutic intervention can be
OL,13,F"transformative" and prevents higher
OL,14,Fspends on crisis services in later
OL,15,Flife.
OL,17,F"This is not just a funding issue,
OL,18,Fthis is a moral issue"
