OL,3,CMPs criticise 'negligent' Labour over
OL,4,Ccuts to adoption support
OL,6,FLib Dem MP for Honiton and Sidmouth,
OL,7,FRichard Foord, accused the government
OL,8,Fof a "moral failure", adding: "A
OL,9,Fsystem that claims to protect children
OL,10,Fcannot simultaneously undermine the
OL,11,Fvery services that support their
OL,12,Frecovery."
OL,14,FHe expressed fears that long-term
OL,15,Ftherapy will now become "unaffordable"
OL,16,Fthrough trusted providers, paving the
OL,17,Fway for ones "that we cannot be sure
OL,18,Fof" to fill the gaps left behind.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
