OL,3,CMPs criticise 'negligent' Labour over
OL,4,Ccuts to adoption support
OL,6,FIn response, the government insisted
OL,7,Fthat families will still be able to
OL,8,Fget "a good standard of support"
OL,9,Fthrough the fund, and, where
OL,10,Fnecessary, local authorities can "use
OL,11,Ftheir own funding" to increase the
OL,12,Famount provided.
OL,14,FChildren's Minister, Janet Daby,
OL,15,Facknowledged that the "threshold and
OL,16,Fcriteria" for the ASGSF HAS changed,
OL,17,Fbut "that has changed to enable us to
OL,18,Fensure that we can reach as many
OL,19,Fchildren under this current funding of
OL,20,F#50m".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
