OL,3,CMPs criticise 'negligent' Labour over
OL,4,Ccuts to adoption support
OL,6,FThe minister also recognised that the
OL,7,Fcurrent level of funding is not enough
OL,8,Fto meet expected demand.
OL,10,FBut MPs aren't the only critics of the
OL,11,Fchanges.
OL,13,FCharity Adoption UK said they "will
OL,14,Fhave a direct impact on children and
OL,15,Fyoung people who have had a very tough
OL,16,Fstart in life and deserve the same
OL,17,Fchance to thrive as everyone else."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
