OL,3,CMPs criticise 'negligent' Labour over
OL,4,Ccuts to adoption support
OL,6,FCEO Emily Frith added: "We understand
OL,7,Fthat this isn't just about the Fund `
OL,8,Fit's a consequence of belt tightening
OL,9,Facross government. But it's very short
OL,10,Fsighted at a time when there are more
OL,11,Fadoptive families in crisis than ever
OL,12,Fbefore, and distressing news for
OL,13,Feveryone who has already faced an
OL,14,Fagonising wait to find out whether the
OL,15,FFund will continue to exist at all.
OL,17,F"The government must use the
OL,18,Fforthcoming spending review to make a
OL,19,Fcommitment to build the Fund back up
OL,20,Fto where adopted and kinship children
OL,21,Fneed it to be."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
