OL,6,FThe Chief Executive of charity
OL,7,FKinship, Lucy Peake, similarly said
OL,8,Fthe funding changes are a "devastating
OL,9,Fblow to thousands of kinship families
OL,10,Fwho desperately need this support".
OL,12,F"It has led to further stress and
OL,13,Funcertainty for struggling kinship
OL,14,Ffamilies as each child will now have
OL,15,Ftheir crucial therapy sessions reduced
OL,16,Fby 40%.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
