OL,3,CMPs criticise 'negligent' Labour over
OL,4,Ccuts to adoption support
OL,6,F"We recognise the importance of
OL,7,Fensuring the ASGSF benefits as many
OL,8,Ffamilies as possible, but reducing the
OL,9,Flevel of therapeutic support available
OL,10,Fto each child could have serious
OL,11,Fimplications for kinship families and
OL,12,Fthe state.
OL,14,F"This decision also sits at odds with
OL,15,Fthe government's recent efforts to
OL,16,Fincrease the number of eligible
OL,17,Fkinship families accessing the Fund.
OL,18,FThe increase in demand was completely
OL,19,Fpredictable, but kinship families are
OL,20,Fnow being unfairly punished for this."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
